Component:

"pthread.c"
"run"
"Makefile"
"readme"(This file)

How to execute:

1. type "make all"
2. chmod 777 run
3. type "./run"

Description:

All modules are integrated into pthread.c. As "./run" is entered, the period threads/asynchronous threads/receiver thread will be activated and run.
And all dequeue behavior can be monitor on the display.

The simulation will end when user double-click left button of mouse in 0.5sec. And all data will pop out from each circular-queue. 
Final read/write pointer status of the 2 queues will be showned.
